00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:52,090
Thank you very much.

298
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,420
Ryouji and Takumi

299
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:08,200
press their lips together
as if to affirm their feelings.

300
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:10,270
And they...

301
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:13,040
become one for the first time.

302
00:23:27,520 --> 00:23:28,380
I have no idea...

303
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,500
how to touch Shirasaki-kun

304
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:35,690
who's keeping me at arm's length.

305
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:38,580
I have no idea.

306
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:41,870
(Next episode)

307
00:23:41,870 --> 00:23:44,440
It's been fun
acting in my first drama.

308
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:47,700
I won't force you
to stay in character anymore.

309
00:23:49,020 --> 00:23:51,910
Why do I keep
thinking about Hayama-san?

310
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,460
Can you hold me?

311
00:23:53,992 --> 00:23:55,052
It sounds fun.
